01:20:32,122 --> 01:20:38,220
get it close,

527
01:20:38,300 --> 01:20:42,740
some far.

528
01:20:42,820 --> 01:20:47,380
Now change hands and feel

529
01:20:47,460 --> 01:20:50,960
with the right hand.

530
01:21:41,340 --> 01:21:46,960
Push back your head and ask three times: “Mother,

531
01:21:47,040 --> 01:21:49,940
is this the cool breeze of the Holy Ghost?

532
01:21:50,020 --> 01:21:51,620
Is this the Chaitanya?

533
01:21:52,260 --> 01:21:56,220
Is this the

534
01:21:56,300 --> 01:22:01,330
all-pervading

535
01:22:01,410 --> 01:22:10,803
power of God's love?”

536
01:22:10,883 --> 01:22:17,790
– ask any one of these,

537
01:22:17,870 --> 01:22:20,740
three times.

538
01:22:24,540 --> 01:22:28,360
Now put down your hands

539
01:22:28,440 --> 01:22:36,180
and feel the breeze.

540
01:22:41,580 --> 01:22:47,400
Those who have felt it, on the fontanel bone area and on their hands,

541
01:22:47,500 --> 01:22:49,880
please raise both hands.

542
01:23:06,620 --> 01:23:09,680
I bow to all of you – you are divine people.

543
01:23:16,380 --> 01:23:21,820
Now you have got it;

544
01:23:21,900 --> 01:23:27,600
so beautiful it is.

545
01:23:31,820 --> 01:23:39,721
I don't know how I will leave Bogota tomorrow,

546
01:23:39,801 --> 01:23:43,560
leaving you all here.

